source.hematite comment.line.number-sign.lithos "# Hydraulic manifold body -- feldspar pressure test #1 (the direct"
source.hematite comment.line.number-sign.lithos "# hit): a thick-walled cylinder claim feldspar's v1 family solves"
source.hematite comment.line.number-sign.lithos "# exactly. Exercises: fat margin (Lame closed form wins, FEA never"
source.hematite comment.line.number-sign.lithos "# runs), thin margin (FEA forced through the SAME claim kind),"
source.hematite comment.line.number-sign.lithos "# material record -> property ports (G2), mm/MPa/degC ingest (G3),"
source.hematite comment.line.number-sign.lithos "# E(T) over an environment range (G5)."
source.hematite ""
source.hematite keyword.control.lithos "import"
source.hematite " std.mech.turned (Bore)"
source.hematite ""
source.hematite keyword.other.decl.lithos "part"
source.hematite " ManifoldBody:"
